{"tid":126240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★支那研究最新款列車於曼谷出軌！","createTime":"2017-02-19T07:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T12:20:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9662aba914c8f095e49717ecaac5bed4d1e5965","tid":126240,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.udnbkk.com/data/attachment/portal/201702/18/164821qnuxcxtic83uvxux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.udnbkk.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fportal%2F201702%2F18%2F164821qnuxcxtic83uvxux.jpg&h=4144f63d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【泰國世界日報訊】今天（18日）從清邁開往曼谷的1171次列車在即將到達曼谷挽賜火車站時，突然發生脫軌事故。這輛灰色的列車共有13節車廂，是泰國國家鐵路局剛從中國引進的新型火車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.udnbkk.com/data/attachment/portal/201702/18/164821wxafi83ne3efgqlh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.udnbkk.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fportal%2F201702%2F18%2F164821wxafi83ne3efgqlh.jpg&h=c0802532&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n據悉，1171次列車正準備駛入挽賜火車站，臨近停車站點時，第2節車廂沒有跟隨車頭變更軌道，導致這節車廂輕微脫軌，目前沒有造成人員傷亡。至於具體原因，相關部門表示須進一步調查確認，目前該列車出軌事件，暫未對火車正常運營造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.udnbkk.com/data/attachment/portal/201702/18/164821kmdvcdkqccidehcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.udnbkk.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fportal%2F201702%2F18%2F164821kmdvcdkqccidehcd.jpg&h=07358589&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.udnbkk.com/portal.php?mod=view&amp;aid=214154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.udnbkk.com%2Fportal.php%3Fmod%3Dview%26aid%3D214154&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=993022e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.udnbkk.com/portal.php?mod=view&amp;aid=214154</a>"},{"pid":"8baa6197afbd60cca12fc22b81a49d08900ae3b1","tid":126240,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i31.photobucket.com/albums/c371/gp03s2